  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "Grease a 9x13 inch baking dish with butter.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine ricotta cheese, milk, salt, and black pepper. Mix well until smooth.",
    "Add the shredded American and casserole cheese blends to the bowl. Mix until well combined.",
